          </h2>
          <p>
            This chart opens with Pisces rising, so it meets the world in a intuitive and porous way. The Moon in Capricorn adds an inner tone that feels structured and duty-aware, while mars-venus link becomes one of the clearest storylines in the chart.
          </p>
